text:
Wh-When I put it on,
It looks a little different again...!

Huh, that ribbon,
What happened to it?

Ah... W-Well,
I couldn't tie it properly...

Well, during the stage, the stylist
Will take care of it, so I think it'll be okay.

Can I ask you something for a moment?
Koito, please stay still.

...Okay, good.
It might be a bit crooked, but you get the idea, right?
